cs.LO, cs.CC, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper is about a new logic system called Computability Logic (CoL) and its extension with toggling operators. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely as the paper deals with the complexity of interactive computational problems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is another possible category as the paper discusses the formalism of CoL, which can be seen as a programming language for interactive computation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with interactive computation, which is a fundamental concept in AI. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper introduces new operations on interactive computational problems, which can be seen as data structures and algorithms.
